{
  "stem": "21731.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said, it means that he want to marry me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he will ask you the permission first before anything else, before it gets out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my aunt was flabbergasted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Max-- I will call him, I think, Max now, and not my future husband and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Max came, more or less, at midday, again with an enormous bouquet of flowers for my aunt, and asked the permission to say we engaged.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We sent a telegram to my mother, who had no idea what was going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mention in-- in letters-- I wrote a lot of letters to Vienna-- that I met a gentleman who is called Dr.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maximilian Schutz, who is not very good looking, he's rather ugly, I wrote.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but he takes-- he spoils me very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he seems to very-- be very-- a very kind man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And his mother also took very much to me, and so did his sister, Lucia, who wanted make out of me a-- a lady of the society.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never was, and I never will be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- today I am not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, my mother came home, in Vienna, from her usually Sunday walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She loved to go to the Vienna woods with her embroidery, or with some knitting, or a book, and some sandwiches, and sat down, and-- and when she came home, there was a telegram in the door-- 'Just got engaged to Dr.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maximilian Schutz.' She later-- she told me she had nearly a heart attack, because what she-- her good looking daughter will have a ugly husband?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That can't be done.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't know whether she phoned or it was telegram.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think we phoned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think there were always telegrams going to and fro.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
